ssdate=2019-10-17 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224144700/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/16/politics/nancy-pelosi-trump-twitter-cover-photo/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

